## Introduction
Welcome to Num-Ninja, a coding project that combines financial management with complex visualization. Our platform offers a versatile Money Management module, featuring a currency exchanger and simple and compound interest calculators. In combination with a robust Graphical Visualizer, including bar graphs, pie charts, and line graphs, we empower users to make informed financial decisions with clarity and precision.

## Features
This project contains the following features:
- Money Management (currency exchanger and simple/compound interest calculator)
- Graphical Visualizer for bar graphs, pie charts, and line graphs.

## Prerequisites
 **Install the repo and pycharm, extract the zip file and open it in pycharm.**

##Install
Ensure you have the following dependencies installed:
```bash
pip install matplotlib
pip install tkinter
pip install numpy
pip install Pillow

##Usage
run the **'main.py'** file

